  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="856" ind1="4" ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="s">2200587</subfield>
    <subfield code="u">http://inspirehep.net/record/1503361/files/3a.png</subfield>
    <subfield code="y">00004 The random potential shown in Fig. \ref{fig:3} acquires two families of inflationary flat directions in terms of the canonical  fields $\varphi$ and $\chi$ in the context of the double-attractor model \rf{cosmo22}, \rf{cosmo32}.  The potential is shown for particular values $ \alpha =  \beta = 1/6$.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="856" ind1="4" ind2=" ">
